title: THE Jerry Springer Show 06.18.08
description:
SHE&#039;S RUBBER, I&#039;M REAL!
    -----------------------
    Love with an airhead...literally. Betty-Joe is everything Billy&#039;s ever wanted in a girl, she&#039;s respectful, quiet, a great listener, and plastic! Billy met this "blow-up" girl in jail and he&#039;s loved her ever since, something Fiancee Amanda isn&#039;t too happy about. Next... Glanisha&#039;s tired of another woman getting in the middle of her relationship with Lamont. The only problem, the other woman, Quanisha, happens to be his wife! Finally... It&#039;s Lee, Harvey, Oswald! Lee takes after his father, Oswald, and loves dressing in women&#039;s clothing. Now it&#039;s driving his wife, Brandy, to sleep with his best friend, Harvey! Plus, Jerry welcomes a new security guard to the show ... past guest and crowd favorite, Tiffany.
